text: Keleshwar Mahadev Temple () is a popular temple of the Lord Shiva in the Borao Ka Khera, Rajasthan. There are a couple of temples built on the bank of Gomti River and it is a prominent picnic and tourist destination. == References == Category:Hindu temples in Rajasthan Category:Shiva temples in Rajasthan Category:Mewar Category:Tourist attractions in Udaipur district
title: Keleshwar Mahadev Temple
